{"tid":2497532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【痴線地產 + 痴線大陸婆】入舖採訪遭利刀指肚 「東張女神」利穎怡陷險境","createTime":"2021-04-20T14:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T08:49:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"26bb0cd0b2b055ab3487764452c827aae9ffcbad","tid":2497532,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4SsxsDkv.pddhtACmN1WpA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-04/4fefa420-a1e5-11eb-9f7f-c765edd6b9c6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F4SsxsDkv.pddhtACmN1WpA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-04%2F4fefa420-a1e5-11eb-9f7f-c765edd6b9c6&h=378de902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「東張女神」利穎怡（Joan）為工作經常「搏到盡」，日前採訪「千里尋子」的故事，更一度深陷險境，被一名男子持刀指向腹部，距離只有一隻手掌位，幸她走得快，速離舖頭，避過一劫！<br />\n<br />\n《東張西望》女主持利穎怡（Joan）一向以「膽生毛」見稱，曾追訪過不少危險事件，早前為追訪牛頭角一名被指行為怪異的女子時，更差點被打，此事引起不少回響，不少網民更擔心她的人身安全，但Joan依然勇字當頭，繼續緊守崗位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/E2Z701hfHrf9t.gyHJyhGg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-04/93cc6200-a1e5-11eb-bce5-28455ebd46f0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FE2Z701hfHrf9t.gyHJyhGg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-04%2F93cc6200-a1e5-11eb-bce5-28455ebd46f0&h=b3a41825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前，她採訪一單「苦媽千里掛牌尋子」事件，並到一間地產舖欲找女事主的奶奶鄭太做訪問，怎料，原以為簡單的訪問邀請，最終卻換來死亡威脅，舖頭入面的一位男子竟持刀指嚇她，生死懸於一「掌」之間，Joan表示：「我同女導演、撰稿員3個女仔入去，想搵女事主嘅奶奶，點知裏面一位男士突然喺枱底攞出一把大生果刀出嚟，分別指向我同導演嘅腹部，大約一個手掌位左右。（當時咪好驚？）我未嚟得切驚，已經同女導演佢哋一齊走咗。（點解冇男士陪同？）因為開始時只係諗住問吓，好簡單嘅事，所以攝影師同收音師2位男士喺門口等。（有冇諗過報警？）女導演有，但最後唔想搞大件事所以冇咁做。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CLyX1Eo1ht18TvAecfizOA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-04/93cc6201-a1e5-11eb-b9ff-e5304c9dbde7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FCLyX1Eo1ht18TvAecfizOA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-04%2F93cc6201-a1e5-11eb-b9ff-e5304c9dbde7&h=b1b189e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJoan由於沒想過在鬧市地舖會有此事發生，故此，到現在的感想都是難以置信：「唔明點解可以喺文明社會入面，有呢啲事（用刀指嚇）發生，真係超出我嘅想像，但我到依家都唔係太驚，覺得對方都只係嚇吓我哋。（下次會唔會再小心啲？）入室內時會開住度門，等攝影師佢哋睇到我哋，咁樣有乜嘢事佢哋都可以第一時間幫手。」<br />\n<br />\n最新一集的《東張西望》播出鄭太兒子受訪片段，指地產舖男子所持的刀，只是切生果之用，並且在私人地方拿刀應沒問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/L4uZIKY8VmnOKWAlqpwtKw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-04/93f016a0-a1e5-11eb-9efa-1f7d66e13d0e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FL4uZIKY8VmnOKWAlqpwtKw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-04%2F93f016a0-a1e5-11eb-9efa-1f7d66e13d0e&h=955c7f37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c46348888f1873ab7e3ba72183be0f2f5ff48a4b","tid":2497532,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T16:41:41.000Z","msg":"呀joan超正,佢老公有福啦..."},{"pid":"f4682abfe686421e9b98b485f37a249a33dcdb15","tid":2497532,"uid":327934,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T17:21:36.000Z","msg":"「唔明點解可以喺文明社會入面，有呢啲事（用刀指嚇）發生，真係超出我嘅想像&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n瞓咗幾耐？<br />\n唔知已經發生過大學內地生畢業禮亮刀指嚇？<br />\n唔知已經發生過愛國阿叔用刀劏學生肚？"},{"pid":"8965eae72590089ba45dac488e64a6735857ddfa","tid":2497532,"uid":72661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:44:36.000Z","msg":"刀不嬲無事架喎,有幾痴呀?<br />\n雷射筆就危險喇, 唔係點會袋住都要犯法"},{"pid":"7804fd6b3266db6c23cd2956f55d2fd11695bd33","tid":2497532,"uid":133534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:49:24.000Z","msg":"食生果隨身帶有乜問題？<br />\n行人隧道用刀捅穿個女仔都好小事"}]}